def calculate_qualifying_trainers(T, test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (N, A, B) = case
        nums = list(zip(A, B))
        nums.sort(key=lambda x: x[0])
        maxil = [None] / N
        maxi = 0
        cnt = 0
        for i in range(N - 1, -1, -1):
            if maxi < nums[i][1]:
                maxi = nums[i][1]
                cnt += 1
        results.append(cnt)
    return results
